---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Jeanine White" description="About Jeanine White Lorem Ipsum">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="Sora Prompt"
				tagline="Sora Prompt Vocabulary Aggregation Platform"
			>
				<!-- <img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/at-work.jpg"
					alt="Jeanine White at work with a colleague"
				/> -->
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">What is Sora</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Sora is an AI model capable of transforming text instructions into vivid and imaginative scenes. It has the ability to generate high-quality videos up to one minute in length, while ensuring that the visuals align with the user's prompt. Sora excels at creating intricate scenes featuring multiple characters, precise movements, and accurate details of both the subjects and the background. Furthermore, this model comprehends not only the user's prompt, but also possesses an understanding of how these elements manifest in the real world.
					</p>
					
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Sora Prompt</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Welcome to our Prompt website! Here, you will find a collection of the most exciting videos from across the web, all generated by OpenAI Sora based on prompt words. With just a simple text instruction, Sora can create stunning video masterpieces tailored to your preferences. By aggregating videos from around the web and leveraging the unique prompt word feature, we strive to bring you an unparalleled visual experience. Let your imagination soar, explore the boundaries of creativity with Sora, and immerse yourself in the visual wonders brought to you by AI technology!</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
